5xl mx-auto px-6"><div class="mb-8"><a class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-gold-400 hover:text-gold-300" href="/am/events">← The Pulse</a></div><div class="aspect-[16/9] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-12"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492684223066-81342ee5ff30?w=1600&amp;q=80" alt="Horizon Festival 2026" class="w-full h-full object-cover"/></div><span class="label-mono">Event</span><h1 class="editorial-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl mt-4 mb-6">Horizon Festival 2026</h1><p class="text-xl text-ink-200 font-serif italic mb-6">Two days. Three stages. One horizon.</p><p class="text-lg text-ink-200 font-serif mb-2">8 ሴፕቴምበር 2026</p><p class="text-ink-400 mb-12">Entoto Hills · Addis Ababa<!-- --> · Entoto Natural Park</p><p class="text-2xl text-ink-200 font-serif leading-relaxed mb-8 italic">Our flagship outdoor festival returns — bigger, bolder, more immersive.</p><div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-lg text-ink-200 font-serif leading-relaxed mb-12 whitespace-pre-wrap">Horizon Festival is where the scene gathers. Two days across three stages, featuring both international headliners and Ethiopia&#x27;s most exciting emerging artists. More than music: installations, food curated by top local chefs, and spaces designed for the unexpected.</div><div class="border-t border-ink-800 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4"><a class="btn-primary" href="/am/tickets/checkout?event=horizon-festival-2026">Buy Ticket</a><a class="btn-ghost" href="/am/contact">More inquiries</a></div></article></div><!--$?--><template id="B:1"></template><!--/$--><!--/$--></main><footer class="border-t border-ink-800 mt-32 bg-ink-900/40"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12"><div class="md:col-span-2"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="relative w-7 h-7 flex-shrink-0"><img alt="Groovethiopia Logo" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-contain" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width